---
pageTitle: Additional information
---
<h1 class="heading-xlarge text">{{ pageTitle }}</h1>

<section class="section-border">
  <h2 class="heading-large">Disability and adjustments</h2>
  <div class="form-group">
    <p class="form-label">Do you have a disability?</p>
    <p class="form-hint">For example, dyslexia</p>
    <div class="form-group form-group-compound inline">
      <label data-target="support-panel" for="support-yes" class="block-label">
        <input name="support" type="radio" id="support-yes" aria-controls="support-panel" aria-expanded="false">Yes
      </label>
      <label for="support-no" class="block-label">
        <input name="support" type="radio" id="support-no">No
      </label>
      <label for="support-prefer" class="block-label">
        <input name="support" type="radio" id="support-prefer">Prefer not to say
      </label>
    </div>
    <div id="support-panel" class="toggle-content" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="form-group">
        <p class="form-label">Select from the list or provide details of disability</p>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-01" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-01" type="checkbox">ADHD</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-02" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-02" type="checkbox">Asperger's syndrome</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-03" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-03" type="checkbox">Cerebral palsy</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-04" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-04" type="checkbox">Chronic fatigue syndrome/M.E.</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-05" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-05" type="checkbox">Diabetes</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-06" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-06" type="checkbox">Dyscalculia/dysgraphia</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-07" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-07" type="checkbox">Dyslexia</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-08" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-08" type="checkbox">Dyspraxia</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-09" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-09" type="checkbox">Epilepsy</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-10" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-10" type="checkbox">Hearing difficulties</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-11" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-11" type="checkbox">Mental health problems, eg depression</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-12" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-12" type="checkbox">Musculoskeletal conditions, eg back pain</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-13" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-13" type="checkbox">Visual impairments</label>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="disability-choice-14" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input id="disability-choice-14" type="checkbox">Other</label>
          </div>
        <label id="question4" class="form-label">Enter more information (optional)</label>
        <textarea id="question4" class="form-control" rows="4" data-val-length-max="4000"></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="heading-large">Guaranteed interview scheme</h2>
        <div class="panel-indent">
          <img src="{{assets}}/img/logo-ticks-small-2x.png" width="38" alt="Two ticks - Positive about disabled people logo" class="image-left">
          <p>If you have a registered disability you may be eligible for the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/recruitment-disabled-people/encouraging-applications" target="_blank" rel="external">guaranteed interview scheme</a>.</p>
          <p>If you choose to apply, we may ask you for supporting documents, if available, at a later stage eg medical documents.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="form-label">Would you like to apply under the guaranteed interview scheme?</p>
      <div class="form-group form-group-compound inline">
        <label for="gis-yes" class="block-label">
          <input name="gis" type="radio" id="gis-yes">Yes
        </label>
        <label for="gis-no" class="block-label">
          <input name="gis" type="radio" id="gis-no">No
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <p class="form-label">Will you need adjustments or support for your assessment?</p>
  <p class="form-hint text">
    If you need extra support with your assessment we can offer reasonable adjustments, eg extra time.
  </p>
  <p class="form-hint text">
    We may need to contact you to talk about and agree any adjustments you request.
  </p>
  <div class="form-group form-group-compound inline">
    <label data-target="adjustment-panel" for="adjustment-yes" class="block-label">
      <input name="adjustment" type="radio" id="adjustment-yes" aria-controls="adjustment-panel" aria-expanded="false">Yes
    </label>
    <label for="adjustment-no" class="block-label">
      <input name="adjustment" type="radio" id="adjustment-no">No
    </label>
  </div>
  <div id="adjustment-panel" class="toggle-content" aria-hidden="true">
    <p class="form-label">Please select which adjustments you'll need</p>
      <div>
        <label for="adjustment-choice-01" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input type="checkbox" id="adjustment-choice-01">Time extension, eg 25% or 30% </label>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="adjustment-choice-03" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input type="checkbox" id="adjustment-choice-03">Coloured paper</label>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="adjustment-choice-06" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input type="checkbox" id="adjustment-choice-06">Braille test paper</label>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="adjustment-choice-07" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input type="checkbox" id="adjustment-choice-07">Room alone</label>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="adjustment-choice-09" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input type="checkbox" id="adjustment-choice-09">Rest breaks</label>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="adjustment-choice-12" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input type="checkbox" id="adjustment-choice-12">Reader/assistant</label>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="adjustment-choice-13" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input type="checkbox" id="adjustment-choice-13">Stand up and move around</label>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="adjustment-choice-14" class="block-label block-label-slim"><input type="checkbox" id="adjustment-choice-14">Other</label>
      </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label id="adj-other" class="form-label">Tell us more (optional)</label>
      <span class="form-hint">If you have any adjustment needs which aren't listed, or want to provide more information, tell us here.</span>
      <textarea id="adj-other" class="form-control" rows="4" data-val-length-max="4000"></textarea>
      <!-- <span class="form-hint maxchar-count">4000</span> -->
      <span class="visuallyhidden aria-limit" aria-live="polite"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-indent text">
      <p>If you want to talk about your adjustment needs in more detail, <a href="helpdesk.html">please contact us</a>.</p>
      <p>It's important you let us know this information now, as there won't be another opportunity to do this.</p>
      <p>(But if your situation changes between submitting your application and attending the assessment centre, contact us.)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2 class="heading-large">How did you hear about us?</h2>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="hearAboutUs" class="form-label">Select how you heard about us (optional)</label>
    <select name="campaignReferrer" id="campaignReferrer" class="selectWithOptionTrigger">
      <option value="">-- Choose method --</option>
      <option value="National apprenticeship service">National apprenticeship service</option>
      <option value="notgoingtouni.co.uk">notgoingtouni.co.uk</option>
      <option value="Social media(Twitter/Facebook)">Social media(Twitter/Facebook)</option>
      <option value="Teachers/careers advisors">Teachers/careers advisors</option>
      <option value="Parent/friends/family">Parent/friends/family</option>
      <option value="Current apprentice/current civil servant">Current apprentice/current civil servant</option>
      <option value="Careers fair" class="optionTrigger" data-optiontrigger="hearAboutUsDetail">Careers fair</option>
      <option value="Google">Google</option>
      <option value="Other" class="optionTrigger" data-optiontrigger="hearAboutUsDetail">Other</option>
    </select>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group toggle-content" id="hearAboutUsDetail">
    <label for="hearAboutUsDetailControl" class="form-label">Provide more information (optional)</label>
    <input type="text" id="hearAboutUsDetailControl" class="form-control">
  </div>
</section>

<div class="form-group">
  <a href="apply-check.html" class="button" id="assistanceSave">Save and continue</a>
</div>